Summary: Two white lights very close together, one following the other at high altitiude.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was on a walk.As I was walking I noticed a light in the sky,I thought it was a star.The next time I looked up it was moving toward me from the northwest.I stood in the street watching it.At first I thought it was the space station.But as it went over I noticed it was two lights very close togather in tandam.They were moving very fast.They were at very high altitiude or possably in space.They traveled from the N.W to the S.E.The hole thing lasted about three Min before they traveled out of sight.
